		(descr "Amphenol SMP-MSSB-PCS, SMP MALE SMT smooth-bore vertical PCB receptacle, 50 ohm, DC-18 GHz. Land pattern per the customer outline drawing (SMP-MSSB-PCS, rev D): centre signal pad 0.79 x 1.7, square ground frame 1.24 wide, 5.21 mm overall. Body 5.0 mm square flange, barrel dia 4.19, mates to MIL-STD-348 SMP. Pad 1 = centre signal, pad 2 = ground (shell frame, all four sides). NOTE: the signal pad is fully enclosed by the ground frame, so the channel trace reaches it via a centre via-in-pad routed on B.Cu under the frame (see finalize_board.py); recommend plugged/capped vias or hand-solder at assembly.")
